title: I have not got any of my first week missions for worlds
body: I clicked start missions yesterday and bought the worlds pass. I logged on today to do the first week of missions and the only worlds mission I have is the first win of the day. I do not have any of the first week missions in my tab.

replies.body:
The only missions you should have other than the pass first win of the day are Go TPA!, Go Fnatic! and Go SKT!. The SSW and SSG missions will presumably come later this week.

https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/special-event/learn-more-worlds-season-2018-event#faq
